#. type: multicols
#: sections/resources.tex:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"There are three types of Resources in the game: Gold \\svg{gold}, Building Materials \\svg{building_materials}, and Valuables \\svg{valuables}.\n"
"Resources are spent during the game to expand your \\pagelink{Town}{Town}, to recruit \\pagelink{Units}{units}, and to purchase \\pagelink{spells}{Spells}.\n"
"You can gain Resources from the \\pagelink{Mines}{Settlements and Mines} that you have \\pagelink{Categories}{flagged}, and also by playing Cards and rolling Resource Dice \\svg{resource_die}.\n"
"Whenever a player's Resource Production is increased or decreased, move that Resource's Cube on its production track the appropriate number of spaces.\\par\n"
"\\begin{multicols}{3}\n"
"  \\centering\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"  \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/gold.png}\n"
"  \\imagecaption{Gold \\phantom{Materials}}\n"
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"  \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/building_materials.png}\n"
"  \\imagecaption{Building Materials}\n"
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"  \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/valuables.png}\n"
"  \\imagecaption{Valuables \\phantom{Materials}}"
msgstr ""
"游戏中有三种资源：金币\\svg{gold}、建筑材料\\svg{building_materials}，以及贵重物品\\svg{valuables}。%\n"
"资源会在游戏中用于扩建你的\\pagelink{Town}{城镇}、招募\\pagelink{Units}{单位}，以及购买\\pagelink{spells}{法术}。%\n"
"你可以从你已\\pagelink{Categories}{插旗}的\\pagelink{Mines}{定居点和矿场}获得资源，也可以通过打出牌和掷资源骰\\svg{resource_die}获得资源。%\n"
"每当一名玩家的资源生产增加或减少时，将该资源的方块在其生产轨道上移动相应数量的格。\\par\n"
"\\begin{multicols}{3}\n"
"  \\centering\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"  \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/gold.png}\n"
"  \\imagecaption{金币}\n"
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"  \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/building_materials.png}\n"
"  \\imagecaption{建筑材料}\n"
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"  \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/valuables.png}\n"
"  \\imagecaption{贵重物品}"

#. type: Plain text
#: sections/resources.tex:27
msgid ""
"Players start each Scenario with the number of Resources indicated in that "
"Scenario’s setup.  Resources can also be \\pagelink{Trading}{traded}.  "
"There's no limit to the amount of Resources you can have."
msgstr ""
"玩家在每个剧本开始时拥有该剧本指定数量的资源。资源也可以\\pagelink{Trading}"
"{交易}。你拥有的资源数量没有上限。"

#. type: center
